title: BRIEF-Tiger Global Management Cuts Share Stake In Netflix, Etsy
text:
Feb 14 (Reuters) - Tiger Global Management:
* TIGER GLOBAL MANAGEMENT DISSOLVES SPONSORED ADR STAKE IN WEIBO CORP - SEC FILING‍​
* ‍TIGER GLOBAL MANAGEMENT TAKES SHARE STAKE OF 900,000 CLASS A SHARES IN SWITCH INC​
* ‍TIGER GLOBAL MANAGEMENT CUTS SHARE STAKE IN NETFLIX INC TO 1.8 MILLION SHARES FROM 3.1 MILLION SHARES
* TIGER GLOBAL MANAGEMENT CUTS SHARE STAKE IN ETSY INC BY 45.1 PERCENT TO 4.2 MILLION SHARES
* TIGER GLOBAL MANAGEMENT CUTS SHARE STAKE IN PRICELINE GROUP INC BY 22.9 PERCENT TO 802,612 SHARES
* TIGER GLOBAL MANAGEMENT CUTS SHARE STAKE IN TRANSDIGM GROUP INC BY 41.1 PERCENT TO 1.9 MILLION SHARES
* TIGER GLOBAL MANAGEMENT - CHANGE IN HOLDINGS ARE AS OF DEC 31, 2017 AND COMPARED WITH THE PREVIOUS QUARTER ENDED AS OF SEPT 30, 2017 Source text for quarter ended Dec 31, 2017: ( bit.ly/2HgqmZi ) Source text for quarter ended Sept 30, 2017: ( bit.ly/2zE2sX3 )
